[size=14pt][font=arial black]Xionzixa is a Brand New server I made recently, InsdiaX based, Retro-design, and Kindness of the Players and Staff is what is so far keeping it alive. Since we started it has been hard to get players due to the factor that Hamachi is not really a thing people take genrously but Xionzixa will hopefully become new hope for Hamachi-Based servers all around. Past few years I used Hamachi and found barely any succus in getting enough players to make my server thrive and Xionzixa is the ticket for Hamachi-Based Servers.
